data.description: Single-Family Home that perfectly combines comfort & elegance sits on a  cul-de-sac, backs up to greenbelt, few steps from Inlet views, few min walk from bluff access to Coastal Refuge, nearby bike paths, recreation area, & schools.  Master bedrm on the main flr, as well as a dedicated office space. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the living rm, featuring large windows & cozy fireplace addscozy fireplace adds warmth & character, creating a perfect spot for relaxation & family gatherings. Upstairs you'll find 3 additional bedrooms, each bedroom is designed with comfort and functionality in mind, providing plenty of closet space and natural light. The backyard of this SFH offers a serene outdoor oasis. It's the perfect place for entertaining, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day.
